43
00:03:16,824 --> 00:03:19,413
They seemed real nice.

44
00:03:25,421 --> 00:03:27,108
"Looked a little country".

45
00:03:28,586 --> 00:03:31,032
"Not something you can get in Canterlot".

46
00:03:31,627 --> 00:03:34,446
I'll show you something worthy of Canterlot!

47
00:03:40,845 --> 00:03:42,641
I have to get started right away.

48
00:03:42,642 --> 00:03:44,282
This new design is very ambitious,

49
00:03:44,283 --> 00:03:49,054
