108
00:08:30,853 --> 00:08:32,643
Of course I'll be there.

109
00:08:39,188 --> 00:08:42,604
Looks like we'll be spending a few more days here, Opalescence.

110
00:08:42,605 --> 00:08:47,065
Turns out bumping into Fancy Pants like that was the best thing that's ever happened to me.

111
00:08:47,366 --> 00:08:52,240
