For me?

137
00:11:02,616 --> 00:11:07,677
Dearest Rarity, your presence is requested at the Canterlot garden party tomorrow afternoon.

138
00:11:07,678 --> 00:11:09,933
Yours, Jet Set and Upper Crust!

139
00:11:11,087 --> 00:11:12,983
The Canterlot garden party!

140
00:11:12,984 --> 00:11:16,946
Right next to the Galloping Gala that is the figure event in Canterlot!

141
00:11:18,509 --> 00:11:21,245
But if I go, I'll miss Twilight's birthday...

142
00:11:21,546 --> 00:11:27,571
But if I don't go, my new reputation in Canterlot as a Very Important Pony might be ruined!

143
00:11:27,572 --> 00:11:31,096
