144
00:11:31,097 --> 00:11:33,777
Friend's birthday... Very Important Pony.

145
00:11:36,663 --> 00:11:38,496
It's just too important.

146
00:11:42,355 --> 00:11:47,307
My dear Twilight, I am afraid I won't be able to make it to your birthday party tomorrow.

147
00:11:47,308 --> 00:11:51,440
Because... because poor Opal is quite ill!

148
00:11:51,441 --> 00:11:56,088
